host_templates.alias: Template to check cAdvisor metrics through API
host_templates.name: Cloud-cAdvisor-Api

information.author: Centreon

description.value:
Plugin Pack to monitor cAdvisor through its exporter API :

* Container-Usage (CPU, Memory, ...)
* Container-Disk-IO
* Container-Traffic
* Node-Status

The Container-* Services should be added thanks to the dedicated service discovery rule.

Plugin Pack pour superviser les métriques en lien avec le noeud cAdvisor et les conteneurs associés via l\'API. 

* Container-Usage (CPU, Memory, ...)
* Container-Disk-IO
* Container-Traffic
* Node-Status

Les Services \'Container-*\' doivent être ajoutés au travers de la règle de découverte de services associée.
